<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p data-changed="false" data-paragraphid="3">Youth are invaluable to the future of our society, and we believe each and every one of them deserves to grow up in a healthy environment regardless of their upbringing. EJI actively takes part in fund-raising events and activities held by organisations with the same vision.</p>'=>'<p data-changed="false" data-paragraphid="3">青少年是社会未来的宝贵财富，我们相信，无论他们的成长环境如何，他们每个人都应该在健康的环境中成长。教育国际积极参加具有相同愿景的组织举办的筹款活动。 </p>','<p>As one of Hong Kong\'s leading fine jewellery manufacturers, we have been creating dazzling designs that are rooted in quality, integrity and elegance since 1991.</p><h2>SUPPLY CHAIN</h2><p>Elegance Jewellery International Limited (EJI) is a member of the <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Responsible Jewellery Council</a> (RJC), the world\'s leading standard setting organisation for the jewellery and watch industry. As a committed RJC member, the business practices of our entire business operations, including jewellery supply chain are adhered to the latest <a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/standards/code-of-practices-2019/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RJC Code of Practices</a>, which provides a common standard for social, ethical, human rights and environmental business practices. EJI is dedicated to creating a healthy work environment and ethical jewellery products, and we strongly encourage all of our business partners to implement the common standard across their operations.</p><p>The Responsible Jewellery Council Policy covers:</p><ul><li>Responsible Supply Chain and Human Rights, from mine to retail</li><li>Labour Rights and Working Conditions</li><li>Health, Safety and Environment</li><li>Gold, Silver, PGM, Diamond and Coloured Gemstone Products</li><li>Anti-Bribery and Corruptions</li></ul><p> </p><p>Click to view:<br /><a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/">EJI RJC Certificate</a><br /><a style="font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px;" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IpdkT6Kq071xcWTR6F2DQAksRk3pU-4E/view?usp=drive_link">EJI RJC Annual Report 2024</a></p>'=>'<p>作为香港首屈一指的高级珠宝制造商之一，自 1991 年以来，我们一直以品质、诚信和优雅为根基，创造出令人目眩神迷的设计。</p><h2>供应链</h2><p>优雅珠宝国际有限公司（EJI）是<a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">责任珠宝委员会（Responsible Jewellery Council</a>，简称RJC）的成员，RJC是世界领先的珠宝钟表行业标准制定组织。作为 RJC 的忠实成员，我们整个业务运营（包括珠宝供应链）的商业行为均遵守<a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/standards/code-of-practices-2019/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RJC</a> 最新的《行为准则》，该准则为社会、道德、人权和环境商业行为提供了通用标准。EJI 致力于创造健康的工作环境和符合道德标准的珠宝产品，我们强烈鼓励所有业务合作伙伴在其业务运营中执行该共同标准。  </p><p>责任珠宝业委员会的政策包括</p><ul><li>从矿山到零售，负责任的供应链与人权</li><li>劳动权利和工作条件</li><li>健康、安全与环境</li><li>金、银、PGM、钻石和彩色宝石产品</li><li>反贿赂和反腐败</li></ul><p> </p><p>点击查看：<br> EJI<a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/">RJC 证书</a><br> EJI<a style="font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px;" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IpdkT6Kq071xcWTR6F2DQAksRk3pU-4E/view?usp=drive_link">RJC 2024 年年度报告</a></p>','<p>Since 2010, EJI has gained several Hong Kong business and employer awards, including the Best SME Award, Partner Employer Award, Caring Company Award, and many more.</p>'=>'<p>自 2010 年以来，亿建国际获得了多个香港商业和雇主奖项，包括最佳中小型企业奖、伙伴雇主奖、商界展关怀奖等。</p>','COMMUNITY'=>'社区','Learn more'=>'了解更多','Responsible Employer'=>'负责任的雇主','WE ARE A MEMBER OF'=>'我们是','Youth Philanthropy'=>'青年慈善事业','editor-text-editor-d572eb8'=>'<p>作为香港首屈一指的高级珠宝制造商之一，自 1991 年以来，我们一直以品质、诚信和优雅为根基，创造出令人目眩神迷的设计。</p><h2>供应链</h2><p>优雅珠宝国际有限公司（EJI）是<a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">责任珠宝委员会（Responsible Jewellery Council</a>，简称RJC）的成员，RJC是世界领先的珠宝钟表行业标准制定组织。作为 RJC 的忠实成员，我们整个业务运营（包括珠宝供应链）的商业行为均遵守<a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/standards/code-of-practices-2019/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RJC</a> 最新的《行为准则》，该准则为社会、道德、人权和环境商业行为提供了通用标准。EJI 致力于创造健康的工作环境和符合道德标准的珠宝产品，我们强烈鼓励所有业务合作伙伴在其业务运营中执行该共同标准。  </p><p>责任珠宝业委员会的政策包括</p><ul><li>从矿山到零售，负责任的供应链与人权</li><li>劳动权利和工作条件</li><li>健康、安全与环境</li><li>金、银、PGM、钻石和彩色宝石产品</li><li>反贿赂和反腐败</li></ul><p> </p><p>点击查看：<br> EJI<a href="https://www.responsiblejewellery.com/member/eji-o-b-elegance-jewellery-international-ltd/">RJC 证书</a><br> EJI<a style="font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px;" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IpdkT6Kq071xcWTR6F2DQAksRk3pU-4E/view?usp=drive_link">RJC 2024 年年度报告</a></p>','editor-text-editor-e469b54'=>'<p data-changed="false" data-paragraphid="3">青少年是社会未来的宝贵财富，我们相信，无论他们的成长环境如何，他们每个人都应该在健康的环境中成长。教育国际积极参加具有相同愿景的组织举办的筹款活动。 </p>','editor-text-editor-f6794b3'=>'<p>自 2010 年以来，亿建国际获得了多个香港商业和雇主奖项，包括最佳中小型企业奖、伙伴雇主奖、商界展关怀奖等。</p>','https://h3y8j2unfg-staging.onrocket.site/tag/corporate-social-responsibility/'=>'https://h3y8j2unfg-staging.onrocket.site/zh-hans/tag/%e4%bc%81%e4%b8%9a%e7%a4%be%e4%bc%9a%e8%b4%a3%e4%bb%bb/','text-button-6005be4'=>'了解更多','title-heading-25e790f'=>'负责任的雇主','title-heading-3f5048f'=>'社区','title-heading-833e7d7'=>'我们是','title-heading-e143e59'=>'青年慈善事业','url-button-6005be4'=>'https://h3y8j2unfg-staging.onrocket.site/zh-hans/tag/%e4%bc%81%e4%b8%9a%e7%a4%be%e4%bc%9a%e8%b4%a3%e4%bb%bb/']];
